Well, you might be wondering why I don’t post that often anymore. Those two beautiful girls are the main reason. As they grow older, I spend more and more time with them. My photography has been shifting little by little to the point that now I mainly only take photos and videos of them. I’m sure I’ll get back to doing more landscapes at some point. But for now, I plan to keep capturing beautiful moments in my daughters life as much as I can. #familytime #familyphotography #nikonz7ii #cinematic #cinematicvideo #bigsur
